I've seen people turn them into lamps (using them as the base), I've seen
people convert them into clocks, saw one guy make a sundial out of his ...
my Dad uses one to prop the back door of the garage open ... I even saw one
that was chrome plated and made into a trophy.

I say, cut the middle out of it, oh say about a 4-5 inch diameter hole and
then use it for a Christmas tree stand.  :c)

